Item Name: Mechanix Wear Specialty 0.5mm Covert Md
Web Item Name: Mechanix Wear Specialty 0.5mm Covert Tactical Gloves Covert Black M
Web Item Description:
Precision feel and high dexterity are synonymous with 0.5mm palm protection. Our Specialty 0.5mm Covert shooting gloves are built to deliver natural feel and lightweight hand protection in an anatomical design. 0.5mm AX-Suede provides the perfect blend of tactile control and protection in the field or at the shooting range. Breathable TrekDry conforms to the back of your hands to reduce heat build-up and expandable flex joints improve trigger finger mobility for smooth manipulation.

Features:

  • Low-profile Thermoplastic Rubber (TPR) closure provides a secure fit to the wrist.
  • Lightweight TrekDry conforms to the back of the hand to reduce heat build-up and perspiration.
  • Anatomical stitch darts conform to the natural curvature of the hand to create a precision fit.
  • Expandable flex joints improve trigger finger mobility.
  • High-dexterity 0.5mm AX-Suede™ provides precision feel and high dexterity.
  • Nylon carrier loops.
  • Machine washable.

Item Name: Alps Grand Slam (Standard)

The ALPS Grand Slam Turkey Vest is the ultimate turkey hunting vest on the market today.   • Five shell loops
  • Hydration compatible
  • Large game bag
  • Two side/water bottle pockets
  • Two mesh zippered pockets inside of vest
  • Side compression straps adjust to different body types

Item Name: Alps Impact Pro Vest
Web Item Name: Alps Outdoorz Impact Pro Turkey Hunting Vest Mossy Oak Original Bottomland
Web Item Description:
The Impact Pro has all the innovative features and essential conveniences of the original Impact with a series of bolstering upgrades that the serious turkey hunter will appreciate. The sit-anywhere design of the flip down seat now features a 1" molded and ergonomic foam design with dual-aluminum stays that is ideal for long sits. Both front panels feature molded pockets for added protection for your calls and gear. Each panel also includes a series of MOLLE webbing to allow you to customize your loadout with a number of different ALPS accessories. Speaking of accessories included with the Impact Pro is a redesigned box call pocket and an accessory ThermaCELL pocket both removable and both able to be mounted to either of the front panels.

Reinforced double and triple stitching ensures both comfort and durability when you need it most. Enjoy your hunt with this premium turkey vest and its XL game bag decoy stake pocket 8 gear pockets including one oversized rear storage pocket contoured shoulder strap design and many more features aimed to please the hardcore turkey enthusiast.

Item Name: Bloodline Dog Vest  Optifade Marsh L
Web Item Name: Rig'Em Right Bloodline Elite Dog Vest Optifade Marsh L
Web Item Description: The Bloodline Elite Dog Vest from Rig'Em Right Waterfowl offers the utmost protection for your most reliable hunting partner. The unique 3-layer construction of the upper material consists of 3mm neoprene gives a  next to "skin" for warmth and comfort. A thin layer of foam for added flotation and an outer layer of heavy-duty canvas for protection from brush and briers. Also features 5mm neoprene throughout the chest for flexibility and warmth and a sturdy braided handle to help you buddy back in the blind. This vest has a more athletic cut around the neck and between the front legs to provide better mobility without rubbing and bunching. Heavy duty zipper with velcro closure over zipper.
Manufacturer: AdvenTec LLC dba Rig Em Right Outdoors

Item Name: Higdon Versa Vest (MO Original Shadowgrass)
Web Item Name: Momarsh Versavest Dog Vest Mossy Oak Original Shadowgrass
Web Item Description:
One Vest that REALLY fits every gun dog - for LIFE! Say goodbye to dangerous ill-fitting dog vests forever. MOMARSH's team of professional designers vets and sporting dog professionals have spent years engineering the world's best dog vest with the mission to do just one simple thing... FIT YOUR DOG.  With its Ultra-strong premium hook and loop adjustments The MOmarsh Versa-Vest properly fits your dog and changes with its shape and size over its lifespan. Six points of multi-directional adjustability ensure proper fit and sizing. Tough rubberized chest panel for ultimate protection. Stow-away handle and leash anchor. The MOmarsh Versa-Vest can be adjusted to be smaller or larger than any waterfowl dog vest on the market. Fits any dog from 35 to 100+ LBS. No Measuring No Cutting No Guessing.  Once the vest is initially adjusted to fit your dog properly simply use the over-sized zipper to take it on and off. No additional adjustments should need to be made until your dog changes shape or size.  Interchangeable cover panels available in other colors (sold separately) are removable replaceable and machine washable. Gore Optifade Waterfowl Marsh cover panels included. The Innovative Versatile Extraordinary Momarsh Versa-Vest. Engineered by Veterinarians Hunters and Sport-Dog professionals to FIT EVERY DOG... FOR LIFE.  

VERSATILE. ONE VEST THAT FITS EVERY SPORTING DOG.

Features:

  • VERSA-VEST can be adjusted to be smaller or larger than any existing sporting dog vest on the market. Fits any dog from 35 to 100+ LBS.
  • BUILT TO REALLY FIT YOUR DOG. 6 points of multi-directional adjustability to ensure proper fit and sizing. Ultra-strong premium hook and loop adjustments. Changes with the shape and size of your dog over its lifespan.
  • SAFE. Helps dog retain body heat in cold or wet conditions. Tough rubberized chest panel for ultimate protection where your dog needs it most. The Built in premium paracord handle and metal leash loop can stow away when not needed.
  • RUGGED. Built tough with high-quality 5mm rubberized Neoprene and water-repellent coated 600D poly fabric.
  • CUSTOMIZABLE. Interchangeable VERSA-VEST PANELS are available in a variety of colors. Panels are removable replaceable and machine washable (sold separately). 

Specifications:

  • One Vest that REALLY fits every gun dog
  • Engineered by Veterinarians
  • Helps dog retain body heat in cold or wet conditions.
  • Six points of multi-directional adjustability
  • Tough rubberized chest panel
  • No Measuring No Cutting No Guessing
  • Fits most dogs from 35 to 100+ lbs
  • Gore Optifade Waterfowl Marsh camo

When cool-weather conditions call for core warmth the Santiam Insulated Vest has you covered. It’s as stylish as it is functional and guaranteed to keep you warm without restricting your movement.

The Santiam Insulated Vest is durable water-resistant and offers the perfect balance between weight and warmth making it perfect for running early morning drills at the range setting up your treestand or hanging trail cameras in preparation for your next big hunt. The 20D ripstop DWR coated fabric protects you from the wind and keeps you dry in a light rain so you stay comfortable when conditions take a turn for the worse. Plus with 60 GMS of lightweight insulation this vest can be worn on its own or as an insulating layer for year-round warmth.

When temperatures drop keep warm and keep moving with the Santiam Insulated Vest whether you’re at the range in the field or out on the town.

Item Name: Moultrie Run N Gun 200-RT Edge Turkey Vest
Web Item Name: Knight & Hale Run N' Gun 200 Turkey Vest Realtree Edge
Web Item Description:
You'll know the instant you put on the Run N' Gun 200 that it isn't the typical hunting vest. First you can guarantee a good fit thanks to its 10-point adjustment system. With adjustments from the shoulders to your chest belly and lumber the Run N' Gun 200 is designed to stay in place without bagginess. This means you won't get constantly caught on limbs and any gear won't cause the vest to shift.

At just 1.5 lbs. the Run N' Gun 200 is one of the lightest on the market; you'll hardly know its there. The cinching system keeps the comfy removable six-layer cushioned seat against your butt for an easy sit-down or you can tuck it out of the way when it's not needed. Its built-in 198-cubic-inch backpack is also bladder compatible.

For gear storage the vest features four zippered pouches and five additional pockets for easy access to pot calls box calls strikers diaphragms your phone and any other accessory a turkey hunter could need. The incorporated MOLLE system allows for added pouches and more. You'll also get a decoy sling. Using a slip knot around the decoy's neck and a set loop around the tail the decoy sling can be quickly thrown over your head to keep decoy(s) secure againt your back while you chase birds.

This model comes in Realtree EDGE.

  • Better fit with less weight at just 1.5 lbs.
  • 10-point adjustment system for optimal fit
  • Hold-tight cinching seat system
  • Open construction allows for breathability keeping you cooler
  • Removable six-layer cushioned seat
  • 198-inch-cubic backpack with bladder compatibility
  • Numerous pockets slots and an integrated MOLLE system for carrying accessories
  • Weight: 1.5 lbs.
  • Camo pattern: Realtree EDGE
  • Integrated backpack: 198-cubic-inch
  • Multiple pockets for calls accessories and more
  • Removable seat cushion
  • Includes decoy sling
  • MOLLE system connections

Carry efficiently and hunt smarter with the Run N’ Gun 300 from Knight & Hale. 

This model comes in Mossy Oak Original Bottomland camo.

  • 375-cubic-inch backpack with bladder compatibility and quick-access zipper
  • 9 zippered pockets on the front

Not a minimalist? Bring it all with the Run N’ Gun 300 Turkey Vest from Knight & Hale. This vest is the pinnacle for the hunter that likes to hunt efficiently prepared and coming in at just 2.5 lbs. you’ll hardly notice it as you trek the turkey woods.

The Run N’ Gun 300 offers an immense level of storage. Featuring nine zippered pockets a 375-cubic-inch backpack capable of holding a water bladder designated spaces for pot calls mouth calls a box call strikers 12/20/410 gauge shotgun shells a Thermacell a phone and a water bottle for good measure – the question isn’t “What should I leave behind?” it’s “Why should I leave anything behind?”

The semi-rigid back and six-layer cushioned seat offer tremendous support whether you’ve found your spot for the morning or need to find a nearby tree quickly – and with 10-points of adjustment you can be sure it will stay true to form from start to finish. Carry efficiently and hunt smarter with the Run N’ Gun 300 from Knight & Hale. 

This model comes in Mossy Oak Full Foliage camo.

  • Large carrying capacity to weight ratio at just 2.5 lbs.
  • 10-point adjustment system for optimal fit
  • Hold-tight cinching seat system
  • Removable six-layer cushioned seat
  • 375-cubic-inch backpack with bladder compatibility and quick-access zipper
  • 9 zippered pockets on the front

Item Name: NOMAD AMBUSH CAMO LS MO BOTTOMLAND L
Web Item Name: Nomad Ambush Camo Long Sleeve Shirt Mossy Oak Bottomland L
Web Item Description: New school tech with old school looks the Ambush shirt sets itself apart by delivering incredible performance while still looking sharp. Honed over years of hunting in the South our Ambush shirt is purpose built for guys that get after it. The lightweight UPF 30+ synthetic fabric is built with inherent stretch that allows full range of motion with shouldering a shotgun or drawing a bow. Laser perforation venting throughout the back and total wicking performance will keep you cool and comfortable when you get that response to your call and the fever starts to kick in. The integrated eyewear wipe has incredible utility when you need to clean lenses whether its binos rangefinders or scopes in the field to your sunglasses for the drive home. The Ambush shirt is a woods hunter classic made better.

The Browning VCI Gun Sock is one of our top sellers. Browning’s VCI (Vapor Corrosion Inhibitor) Gun Sock seals out moisture. VCI penetrates into the smallest crevices where oils cannot reach driving out moisture. Provides full protection by forming an enclosure around your firearm from muzzle to butt stock.

The "safe" solution. The VCI Sock when used in a safe or cabinet will offer additional protection to all metal items in the enclosed area.

A few important facts:

  • Browning’s VCI (Vapor Corrosion Inhibitor) Gun Sock seals out moisture.
  • The VCI treatment of the fabric penetrates into small areas and crevices of your firearm to drive out moisture. Even areas difficult for oil to reach.
  • Since it is a sock with full coverage it surrounds your firearm to protect every part from corrosion and rust and from inadvertent light touches against other guns or when moving your gun in and out of your safe.
  • Of course the VCI is especially effective when used in a gun safe or display cabinet.
  • The drawstring closure helps trap in the VCI for maximum effectiveness.
  • VCIs are sometimes also referred to as Volatile Corrosion Inhibitors. They are proven as one of the most effective ways to inhibit corrosion for sensitive metal components -- with superior results for firearms. Learn more at Wikipedia:  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volatile_corrosion_inhibitor

The Early Season Hooded Shirt is designed with hot late summer/early fall days in mind. And variables like a breeze from the north or a blanket of clouds can keep the weather unpredictable all day long. Of course this just underscores the importance of proper layering and the need of the Monroe 1/4 Zip Shirt.

This 2 layer piece is constructed with a tough dura knit fleece outer and a warm fleece inner surface for the perfect combination of durability warmth and stretch-enhanced comfort. The addition of a DWR coating offers water resistance making the Monroe extra versatile as both an outer piece in warmer conditions and an ideal insulation layer under a parka.

The Field Pro pant is versatile and comfortable making it a great addition to your hunting gear selection. Engineered with a 2L soft shell stretch fabric this pant is built for warmer weather waterfowl hunting with the right combination of durability wind and water resistance and just the right amount of stretch to optimize comfort. A DWR coating adds a level of water resistance. The soft inner lining adds comfort and warmth.

The Field Pro pant includes front and rear pockets plus a pair of cargo pockets on the thighs to keep your gear within easy reach. 13" long leg vents with zippered closures help keep you cool when the weather warms up or your activity level rises. The comfortable cut allows for a base layer to be comfortably worn making the Field Pro pant an excellent outer layering piece for cooler drier weather.

Item Name: PNT DUTTON HYBRID OVIX 34
Web Item Name: Browning Dutton Hybrid Pant Ovix 34
Web Item Description:
With winter weather on the horizon weather during fall and late season hunts is unpredicatable. To meet the challenges of staying warm and dry in changing conditions we recommend layering with the Dutton Hybrid Pant. The Berber fleece fabric on the inside provides tremendous warmth and thee smooth faced outer shrugs off brush and rough country. A bit of stretch in the fabric adds mobility.

By giving you a raised back and suspenders the Dutton Hybrid Pant melds the comfort and extra warmth of a bib with the lighter weight of a pant. So whether you're sitting for hours in a tree stand or on a rocky incline the raised rear panel is there to keep drafts from running up your back. Suspenders further eliminate drafts and add extra comfort while belt loops allow for additional adjustment as well as a place to hand your hunting knife and ammunition.   

The Dutton Pant provides a comfortable fit that is built for layering without binding. Articulated knees offer additional flex when walking. Side zippers make it possible to slip the pants on over boots easily. 

Multiple pockets offer secure gear storage. A pair of thigh cargo pockets are mounted to the front for improved access when sitting.

Multiple pockets offer secure gear storage. A pair of thigh cargo pockets are mounted to the front for improved access when sitting.

Item Name: Browning UPLAND DENIM Pant CHOC/TAN 32X32
Web Item Name: Browning Upland Denim Pant Chocolate Tan 32x32
Web Item Description:
Denim and Hunting are here to stay.

Denim hs been around for a long time. And the gold rush of 1849 even made them famous. But these are not those pants. exactly. Browning Upland Denim Pants give you the time-honored feel and comfort of denim with the thorn and thistle defeating benefits of a tough twill lower. Yes the fit is superb. And the comfort will surprise you. But most of all they can take what your upland hunt dishes out. They are decidedly not constructed with space-age materials. They are the best of traditional designs for the ordinary days of hunting that you love the most. They look pretty good but you won't wear these to a night on the town unless it's some delightful little cafe in the middle of nowhere after another great upland hunt. 

Features:

  • Rugged 10 oz. cotton upper
  • Brush-resistant rough twill lower
  • Four-pocket design
  • Articulated knee darts aid flexibility
  • Regular Fit

Item Name: JKT WW RAIN SHELL MOBL S
Web Item Name: Browning Rain Shell Jacket Mossy Oak Bottomland S
Web Item Description:
Duck hunting and rain are synonymous. Good thing there's a Rain Shell Jacket in the Browning Wicked Wing line up. The Rain Shell Jacket is made to keep you dry and comfortable while waiting for the birds to fly even when nature isn't  cooperating. The key feature is the reliable Pre-Vent Plus membrane that rivals the performance and durability of leading waterproof/breathable garments. Fully-taped seams ensure that these often overlooked points of entry are sealed against the elements. The outer shell fabric is tough enough to shrug off brush and has an additional water-resistant DWR coating that provides greater protection from moisture. If the rain subsides this jacket is light enough to stuff away inside its own pocket. It also features water-resistant zippers on the front and hand pockets. The three-piece hood is adjustable for added comfort and to optimize performance in the elements. 

The Rain Shell Jacket can be worn alone but is also ideal for use over an insulating layer in colder wet weather. As part of the Browning X-Change System Wicked Wing insulating garments can be zipped in to create a garment that is optimized for the conditions at hand. It also features water-resistant zippers on the front and hand pockets. The three-piece hood is adjustable for added comfort and to optimize performance in the elements. 

Features:

  • Water/windproof fabric with fully-taped seams
  • Pre-Vent Plus membrane is highly breathable and waterproof with 8000 cubic inch moisture transfer rate
  • Adjustable hood
  • Water-resistant zipper hand pockets
  • Water-resistant front zipper with internal storm flap
  • Stuffs into left-hand pocket
  • Elastic adjustable hem
  • Hook and loop cuff closure
  • X-Change System compatible

Web Item Description:
With a water-resistant windproof  3-layer fabric the Browning Field Pro Vest is designed to act as both an outer layer and a versatile mid layer. As an outer layer the stretchy quiet shell fabric features a windproof membrane that protects from chill winds and light moisture. The micro-check fleece lining traps heat effectively to keep your core warm when used as part of a layering system.

Features:

  • 3L windproof and highly water-resistant face fabric with micro-check ?eece backer
  • Full front zipper
  • Extra tall collar with beard guard
  • Zipper Napoleon pocket on chest
  • Two zipper handwarmer pockets
  • Silvadur technology provides long-lasting odor control
  • X-Change System comatible

Item Name: VST WW INSULATED MOBL S
Web Item Name: Browning Insulated Vest Mossy Oak Bottomland S
Web Item Description:
Keep your core temperature up with the Wicked Wing Insulated Vest. This vest features 133 grams of premium PrimaLoft Silver insulation making it ideal as an outer later in cooler temperatures and a superior insulating layer. Quilting in the lower half prevents the insulation from migrating. The outer shell is a durable ripstop nylon that is water and wind resistant. The adjustable hood is removeable. Fleece lined handwarmer pockets are located at the hips and also on the chest when wearing waders.

As part of the Browning X-Change System the Insulated Wader Jacket can be zipped into a waterproof outer shell to provide all-weather protection.

Features:

  • 2L polyester honeycomb ripstop fabric
  • Windproof main body
  • 133 grams of PrimaLoft Silver insulation
  • Quilted lower body
  • Adjustable removable hood
  • Fleece-lined zippered handwarmer pockets
  • Zippered chest pocket
  • Elastic adjustable hem
  • Water-resistant front zipper with integrated storm flap
  • X-Change System compatible

  • Regular Fit

Item Name: VST PACKABLE PUFFER OVIX S
Web Item Name: Browning Packable Puffer Hooded Vest Ovix S
Web Item Description:
Designed to be part of your clothing arsenal all year long the Packable Puffer Hooded Vest sets its sights on both warmth and compressibility. The combination of a tough polyester micro-ripstop fabric and PrimaLoft Silver blended down insulation make for a vest that is highly compactible. In warmer conditions the Packable Puffer Vest stows away virtually unnoticed in your pack until called upon to take away after-dark chill or an unplanned breeze in the high country. In cold weather it becomes a great mid layer.  

Features:

  • 100% polyester micro-ripstop fabric is highly compactible and lightweight
  • PrimaLoft Silver down blend (650 fill power) with fluorocarbon-free water repellent treatment
  • Attached hood with internal adjustments
  • Elastic binding on waist hem
  • Zipper handwarmer pockets
  • Water-resistant front zipper with internal storm flap and chin guard
  • Vest stuffs into back neck yoke overlay
  • Silvadur technology provides long-lasting odor control

Item Name: GLV WW DECOY MOBL M
Web Item Name: Browning Decoy Glove Mossy Oak Bottomland M
Web Item Description:
Imagine warm dry hands... If you've picked up decoys from the marsh and never used a waterproof gauntlet-style decoy glove you're missing out. The extended gauntlet is designed to keep the water that drips off of the decoys cables and weights from running up your sleeves and into regular gloves when you're setting out and picking up your decoys. An adjustable elastic closure at the top of the gauntlet further prevents water entry.

This Decoy Glove from Browning is rugged and waterproof with a polyester double weave fabric and leather palm overlay. PrimaLoft Silver insulation keeps your hand warm even after plunging into icy waters. A neoprene cuff with adjustable tab provides a secure fit.. The fully articulated design offers an excellent grip and maximizes dexterity. 

Features:

  • Fully waterproof polyester double-weave fabric with highly durable wrist to elbow length gauntlet
  • 25 gram PrimaLoft Silver insulation
  • SILVADUR technology provides long-lasting odor control
  • High-traction leather palm
  • Neoprene wrist
  • Adjustable elastic cord at the top of the gauntlet
  • Structured hook and loop wrist clasp
  • Fully articulated design
  • Pairing clip attachments
